Refactor OrderPayment calculation and improve code documentation
Refactored the calculate method in OrderPayment to optimize database queries, and included the carrier price in the total price calculation. Also, added detailed documentation for each method and improved the accounting report layout in Platform.

FIX: Update payment logic to handle precision in OrderPayment
Refactored the condition for missing payments in OrderPayment layout to check if the missing amount is more than 0.01 instead of less than 0.01. This handles the precision issue for payments and enhances accuracy.

FIX: Refactor product quantity increment/decrement and payment calculations
Updated product quantity increment/decrement in ShopProducts model by removing hardcoded increment value. Modified payment calculations in OrderPayment layout to improve accuracy, handling multiple products in an order for total price calculation. Fixed error response status in the DeviceController.
